description.narrative: This activity (Arab Women Enterprise Fund) is a component of Arab Womens Enterprise Fund reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £9,798,400. This component benefits Middle East, regional, and works in the following sector(s): Women's equality organisations and institutions, Employment creation, Business Policy and Administration. , with the following implementing partners: DAI Europe. The start date is 01-07-2015 and the end date is 31-10-2020.
